Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.46,0:00:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想打從心裡大叫一句\N好想快點見到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.48,0:00:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信總有一天\N一定能相遇相知永結連理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.16,0:00:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起步走出\N希望妳能追著我的背影而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.61,0:00:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我孤單一人只為等候妳的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落英繽紛的春日午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.56,0:01:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將祈禱轉為誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.57,0:01:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願妳不會忘記最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.77,0:01:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠閃亮動人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.49,0:01:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好遲鈍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.03,0:01:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為五代很體貼\N我以為他會好好珍惜我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.64,0:01:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我萬萬沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.81,0:01:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他居然會跟那種人在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.08,0:01:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好傻哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.28,0:02:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的''那種人''是指誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.09,0:02:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一刻館的朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.79,0:02:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.93,0:02:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我親眼看見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.33,0:02:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人從賓館走出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.37,0:02:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#92小津江結婚!\N五代的愛直到永遠?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.22,0:02:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能,完全無法想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.20,0:02:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去勾引五代了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管朱美是那種個性\N但還不至於會開這種玩笑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.24,0:02:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去勾引他了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.64,0:03:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去勾引他了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.59,0:03:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員遲遲不回來耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.89,0:03:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊…啊,歡迎光…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-哎呀\N-啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.58,0:03:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.85,0:03:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接回一刻館不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.82,0:03:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,有點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在大家一定都在等妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,是啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.20,0:04:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.94,0:04:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不好意思回去\N因為給大家添了很多麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.31,0:04:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真傻啊\N沒有人會在意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.21,0:04:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫他們來吧\N他們應該都在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.72,0:04:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,妳聽我說\N我還沒說要回去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.72,0:04:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員在我們店裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有說要回去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想問妳一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.37,0:05:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.57,0:05:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我在車站前遇到小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.44,0:05:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳遇到小津江?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.88,0:05:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,她告訴妳了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.45,0:05:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟五代從賓館出來的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.46,0:05:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢?這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.26,0:05:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.25,0:05:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.15,0:06:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她從剛才就這樣動也不動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.16,0:06:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的跟朱美去了賓館嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這本來就是真的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.83,0:06:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,我是清白的\N我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.17,0:06:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人…我最討厭了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不當管理員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.92,0:06:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,我真的什麼都沒做\N請妳相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.99,0:06:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用再解釋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.66,0:06:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你高興跟誰上床就儘管去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.16,0:06:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真相到底是怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.50,0:06:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算跟她說什麼都沒做\N她也不會相信吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.07,0:06:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我跟五代身體連在一起\N心也是分開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.61,0:06:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以跟沒上過床是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.88,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰跟妳連在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.21,0:07:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了,不用再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.32,0:07:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個爛人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去當朱美的小白臉好了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.94,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣,你打啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.97,0:07:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你儘管打啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.81,0:07:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的問心無愧的話\N我就讓你打啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.88,0:07:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳實在太不講理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.82,0:07:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒出息、卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.72,0:07:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩女人、拈花惹草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.82,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,低級的爛男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.60,0:07:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少聽我解釋一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.52,0:08:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請買單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳實在太丟臉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.66,0:08:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了一個手都沒有握過的男人\N又哭又鬧的,妳是怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.53,0:08:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的品味可沒有差到\N會跟妳這麼麻煩的女人搶男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.71,0:08:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,狗和行李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.55,0:08:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.69,0:08:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少把外套送去給她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.62,0:08:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外頭天氣很冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.89,0:08:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要命,麻煩死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.86,0:08:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還敢說呢\N妳是這場風波的罪魁禍首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂下雨之後\N泥土才會變得堅硬嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.51,0:09:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要辭職,我不當管理員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了每天擔心這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.75,0:09:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽我說\N我跟朱美真的沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.19,0:09:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要在這種地方談這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.96,0:10:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道我可能太多疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.01,0:10:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.94,0:10:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩人之間\N的確什麼關係都還沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微再聊一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.46,0:10:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該去上班了不是嗎,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.26,0:10:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就好,邊走邊聊也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.90,0:10:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近發生的事全都是誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要說清楚就沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.78,0:10:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳卻完全不相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.85,0:10:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,這麼說都是我的錯囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是,只不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.16,0:11:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,妳忘了最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.03,0:11:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的事?你指的是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.07,0:11:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.81,0:11:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.65,0:11:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從第一次見到妳時,就一直…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也是,以後也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.29,0:11:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以,如果妳不相信\N我對妳的感情的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.46,0:11:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了,你怎麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.40,0:11:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在突然跟我說這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來好像是在敷衍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.97,0:11:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳說,我該怎麼做才對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.64,0:11:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼跟其他的女人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.51,0:11:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那種本事\N可以同時和那麼多女人交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.42,0:12:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.05,0:12:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳還不懂嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.52,0:12:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼裡只有妳一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.42,0:12:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只有妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.72,0:12:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇遇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.23,0:12:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有什麼心事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.46,0:12:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才就一直悶悶不樂的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.83,0:12:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.93,0:12:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.28,0:13:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…五代現在過得怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.22,0:13:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在也是要死不活的\N因為被妳甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.05,0:13:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,真討厭\N其實被甩的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.13,0:13:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這我還是第一次聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.46,0:13:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代竟然做出這麼可惜的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.37,0:13:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為五代跟朱美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.77,0:13:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賓館的事對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.51,0:13:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代只是被叫去\N幫她付賓館的錢而已?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.15,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對,只是這樣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.13,0:14:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼裡只有妳一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只有妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.18,0:14:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賭氣賭得太過頭了\N突然覺得好累哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.88,0:14:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明希望自己能坦率一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更坦率一點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.50,0:15:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來來來,裡面坐裡面坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.47,0:15:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在折價大優待,超便宜的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.54,0:15:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位老闆,超值大優待\N漂亮的美眉等著你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.91,0:15:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.04,0:15:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你這個混蛋\N知不知道現在幾點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.12,0:15:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.02,0:15:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有一件很重要的事\N非得馬上處理不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.89,0:15:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.79,0:15:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被我猜中了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.43,0:15:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.24,0:15:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,真拿你沒輒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人在等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.94,0:15:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.82,0:15:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,部長來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,你好慢哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.15,0:15:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.44,0:16:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她來做什麼的呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,跟人家玩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.41,0:16:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我摺色紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.68,0:16:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起對不起,稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.65,0:16:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,打擾到你工作了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.99,0:16:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?還好啦\N不過,沒想到妳會來找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.99,0:16:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情的真相,我都聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是過去\N幫朱美付賓館的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.23,0:16:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟朱美之間\N根本沒發生什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.70,0:16:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,對不起\N我沒有相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.91,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說,應該道歉的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.82,0:17:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,五代,過來一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.96,0:17:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公司內法規第二條\N說來聽聽看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.50,0:17:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,不能把私事帶到職場來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.67,0:17:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.34,0:17:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先是為了馬子的事上班遲到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著又在小孩子面前\N親親熱熱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有親親熱熱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.98,0:17:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是…有件事\N必須跟她說清楚才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分手的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.89,0:17:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就更不能在小孩子面前講了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.73,0:17:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.07,0:17:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖哦,不哭不哭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.60,0:17:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想哄哄他而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.00,0:17:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好哦,乖哦乖哦,不哭不哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.01,0:18:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了,不哭哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.68,0:18:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖哦,乖哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.22,0:18:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,你好厲害哦,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.99,0:18:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定可以成為很棒的褓父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,我放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.63,0:18:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她果然是想來\N跟我重修舊好的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,不跟她講清楚的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只會受到更大的傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳會不會冷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,不冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,我跟妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.11,0:19:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月色好美哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.78,0:19:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,真的很美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.75,0:19:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,我要跟妳講一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.79,0:19:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.23,0:19:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我什麼都還沒講耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.76,0:19:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.97,0:19:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不要討厭我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.21,0:19:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到她對我這麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我非說不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.65,0:19:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再跟妳交往了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.19,0:20:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有喜歡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.46,0:20:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對妳真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.23,0:20:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳恨我的話\N我也覺得那是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.14,0:20:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰?真的是朱美嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是,不是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.92,0:20:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是誰?\N是我不認識的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.86,0:20:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要結婚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.13,0:20:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟那個人結婚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.57,0:20:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒,雖然還沒到那個階段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.64,0:20:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我想跟她結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.54,0:20:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不能再跟妳交往下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.52,0:21:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛,我來見你是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.09,0:21:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得好像鬆了一口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.63,0:21:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.50,0:21:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要結婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.17,0:21:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚?\N是跟上次妳說的高中學長嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.38,0:21:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次見到你跟朱美之後\N我馬上下定決心接受他的求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.52,0:21:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我本來也打算\N不再跟你見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.66,0:21:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在知道是誤會一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.60,0:21:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很討厭分手分得很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.36,0:21:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不希望分手之後被你討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.27,0:21:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們算是扯平了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.15,0:22:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方是個很好的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.85,0:22:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,他人真的很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.26,0:22:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好像很愛我的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.49,0:22:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我覺得可以相信他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.60,0:22:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這裡分手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.23,0:22:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搭計程車回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.50,0:22:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.41,0:22:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.65,0:22:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.22,0:22:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.22,0:22:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是個什麼樣的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.26,0:22:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的人\N是個什麼樣的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.99,0:22:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.43,0:22:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,還是不要說好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.36,0:22:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了,你要保重哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.98,0:23:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.92,0:23:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是個什麼樣的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.52,0:23:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的人\N是個什麼樣的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.22,0:23:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小津江,我喜歡的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.93,0:23:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很會吃醋,是個急性子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.30,0:23:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且愛哭、容易生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.77,0:23:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要看到她的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.27,0:23:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.56,0:23:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.93,0:23:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你終於可以畢業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.93,0:23:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只剩下找到工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.53,0:23:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.97,0:23:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以那個了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.77,0:23:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羨慕死了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.07,0:24:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.67,0:24:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『春天的預感?\N兩人的熾熱心情!』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.14,0:24:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有人想嫁給我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.64,0:24:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.32,0:24:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.45,0:24:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳該知道這不是擦身而過的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.43,0:24:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻也是…woo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.60,0:24:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比我想像中冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.87,0:24:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡一個人獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.51,0:24:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉默不語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.32,0:24:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.12,0:24:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這燭火依偎著的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.26,0:25:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凝視著妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.27,0:25:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試著將至今的謊言吹熄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.04,0:25:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.65,0:25:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.95,0:25:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自我陶醉故弄玄虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.39,0:25:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我行不通…woo
